Firmware is an openssl signed tar file.

Encryption of firmware can be done by executing the following command:
openssl enc -aes-128-cbc -k a0n1ipc -p -in DCS6100LHAx_FW103B03.tar -out DCS6100LHAx_FW103B03.bin

Decryption can be done by:
openssl enc -d -aes-128-cbc -k a0n1ipc -p -in DCS6100LHAx_FW103B03.bin -out DCS6100LHAx_FW103B03.tar

Version of openssl to be used:
OpenSSL 1.0.2l  25 May 2017 (Library: OpenSSL 1.0.2j  26 Sep 2016)


